1
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,920
Shentu

2
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:09,640
What's wrong?

3
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,240
You were dreaming.

4
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,400
Don't tell me an Evil spirit has possessed you too.

5
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,760
Perhaps I'm just a bit tired.

6
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,640
What are you doing with that?

7
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,600
An experiment.

8
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,440
You're experimenting on me?

9
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,000
You...

10
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:23,840
You...

11
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,000
Lao Yao.

12
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,520
Have you ever noticed...

13
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,600
if the victim had fractures in the limbs or throat?

14
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:31,880
No, they didn't.

15
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,360
The killer struck with such great force,

16
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,600
yet it didn't affect his accuracy at all.

17
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,600
Every strike was extremely precise.

18
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,040
Unless it's someone who works with hammers and nails daily,

19
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,160
it would be impossible to achieve.

20
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,120
Exactly.

21
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,600
Wu Tu'an fits that description perfectly.

22
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,400
As a coffin carrier, Wu Tu'an...

23
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,360
often needs to seal coffins.

24
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,000
He handles hammers and nails frequently.

25
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,240
He is indeed very suspicious.

26
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:08,960
But Lao Yao,

27
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,000
Hmm?

28
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,440
do you really believe in the Evil spirit talk?

29
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,400
Not at all.

30
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,520
I only believe the facts before my eyes.

31
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,360
Xiao Lian is dead.

32
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,560
Wu Tu'an was the person closest to her.

33
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,040
And he also had the Coffin Shop's copper key.

34
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,280
And coincidentally, at this very moment,

35
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,080
he has vanished without a trace.

36
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,440
All of this is too much of a coincidence.

37
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,360
Whether it's an Evil spirit or not,

38
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,520
Wu Tu'an...

39
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,240
is highly suspicious.

40
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,040
Are you the coffin carrier, Dong Qiu?

41
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:45,840
It is your humble servant.

42
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,120
Let me ask you.

43
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,680
The victim Xiao Lian's husband,

44
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:49,560
Wu Tu'an...

45
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:50,840
what kind of person is he?

46
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,680
Tu'an is usually a simple, honest man.

47
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,680
He's never had a dispute with anyone.

48
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,240
He works hard,

49
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,120
and speaks little.

50
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,800
How was the relationship between the couple?

51
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:00,880
Was there any animosity?

52
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,280
I've never heard of any animosity.

53
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:04,440
My Lord,

54
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,760
we coffin carriers are looked down upon.

55
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,480
No woman is willing to marry us.

56
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,240
Yet he married a good wife like Xiao Lian.

57
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,120
We were very envious.

58
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:15,360
In this court,

59
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,080
is everything you said true?

60
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,800
Your humble servant dares not speak a word of falsehood.

61
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,480
My Lord,

62
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,800
there is something your humble servant hesitates to say.

63
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:27,720
Speak.

64
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,120
That day before dawn,

65
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,400
before carrying the coffin,

66
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,840
a strange thing did indeed happen.

67
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:51,440
What are you doing?

68
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,440
Brother Dong Qiu.

69
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:53,680
Inside here...

70
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,240
Shut up.

71
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,840
We take money to carry the coffin.

72
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,280
We carry whatever the client buries.

73
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,960
What's inside the coffin is none of our business.

74
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:08,160
Let's go.

75
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:16,640
Why are you standing there?

76
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,480
Hold it down!

77
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,280
Brother Dong Qiu!

78
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,320
What's happening?

79
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,040
Don't ask me, how should I know?

80
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,160
Hold it down tight!

81
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,200
If the client finds out tomorrow,

82
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,560
we won't be able to explain ourselves.

83
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,640
When we carry the coffin tomorrow,

84
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,960
we'll pretend we know nothing.

85
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:54,800
Let's go.

86
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:55,920
Okay.

87
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:57,800
Let's go.

88
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,400
Interesting.

89
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:12,600
According to you,

90
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:15,800
the Evil spirit in the coffin possessed Wu Tu'an,

91
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:16,920
controlled him,

92
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:20,000
and made him nail his loving first wife to death.

93
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:20,800
Is that so?

94
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,200
Your humble servant dares not speak nonsense.

95
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,120
But inside that coffin,

96
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,600
perhaps there really is a Wronged spirit hiding.

97
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:27,840
Oh?

98
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,280
The client, the Sun family...

99
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,920
the one to be buried was their young lady, Miaoling.

100
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,440
That day,

101
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,160
I took the coffin from the Coffin Shop to the Sun family.

102
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,680
But at that time,

103
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,880
Miaoling was not yet dead.

104
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,040
Here is the payment for the coffin.

105
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:45,920
Thank you for your trouble.

106
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,280
You are too kind, sir.

107
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,560
When it is time for the burial,

108
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:50,760
I will send someone to summon you.

109
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:51,600
All right.

110
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,640
After that day,

111
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:17,680
I was curious,

112
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,800
so I asked around.

113
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,320
They said it was called the...

114
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,560
Life-Burning Ritual.

115
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:25,200
Writing someone's birth date on yellow paper under a white candle.

116
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,600
When the candle burns out,

117
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,200
the yellow paper catches fire,

118
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,680
and along that red string,

119
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,240
it burns away the life of the person tied to it.

120
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,240
Absurd.

121
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,760
Your humble servant knows nothing of sorcery.

122
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:39,000
Everything I said, I saw with my own eyes, My Lord.

123
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,680
But you took that coffin from the shop with your own hands.

124
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,520
It was not me.

125
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,920
I do not have the Coffin Shop's copper key.

126
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,960
The copper key was in Wu Tu'an's possession.

127
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,480
We usually work together,

128
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,880
and since Tu'an is a steady man,

129
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,720
the copper key was entrusted to him.

130
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:00,680
You may return for now.

131
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,440
Until the case is concluded,

132
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,760
do not leave Chang'an.

133
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,760
Your humble servant understands.

134
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,880
How much of his story is true?

135
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,560
What do you mean?

136
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:23,640
Do you suspect him?

137
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:27,360
A woman killed by her husband's Life-Burning Ritual...

138
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,440
is indeed worthy of sympathy and pity.

139
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:32,160
It confirms the rumors of Wronged spirits and Evil spirits,

140
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:34,040
while also pointing the finger at the Sun family.

141
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:35,760
My Lord.

142
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:37,600
My Lord!

143
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:38,720
Wu Tu'an has been found.

144
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:39,840
Where is he?

145
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:40,880
He is dead.
